commitResults.messageTitle: Add Level-1 Greet, Echo and Exit
commitResults.messageBody:
Duke will now greet the user, echo any commands entered through the standard
input, and exit when the user types "bye".

Duke now adds user entered commands to an array of commands that
can be displayed using the "list" command.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add functionality to mark tasks as done
commitResults.messageBody:
"done n" will now mark task n as done, and "list" command will
reflect if tasks are done.

commitResults.messageTitle: Edit coding style to follow course coding standards
commitResults.messageBody: Add comments to methods and clean up indentation
